author: Bo Wenze
notes: 薄文泽 / Bo Wenze. 木佬语硏究 / Mulao yu yan jiu (A Study of Mulao). Beijing: 中央民族大学出版社 / Zhong yang min zu da xue chu ban she, 2003.Mulao (木佬), a Kra language, is not to be confused with a Kam-Sui language of the same name (仫佬) which is alternatively called Mulam. Mulao is closely related to Gelao and is spoken in Longli (龙里), Majiang (麻江), Guizhou, China.  However, it is not documented on Ethnologue (see http://lingweb.eva.mpg.de/numeral/Mulao.htm for more information).
